Class ConfigsApi

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.cloud.api.ConfigsApi

  • public class ConfigsApi
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract representation of Configs API endpoint. Provides executors that can be used to handle all config-related requests.
